<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0d9fd263-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s20987"><num value="20987">§ 20987.</num><heading> Consultation with Standards Board and Board of Advisors</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Commission shall carry out its duties under this part in consultation with the Standards Board and the Board of Advisors.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0d9fd264-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/252/tII/s247">Pub. L. 107–252, title II, § 247</ref>, <date date="2002-10-29">Oct. 29, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1692">116 Stat. 1692</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id0d9fd265-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id0d9fd266-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="id0d9fd267-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section was formerly classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s15387">section 15387 of Title 42</ref>, The Public Health and Welfare, prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section.</p>
</note>
